ion: 35 minutes.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-03-25T08:57:12.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://damienbod.com/2021/03/23/setting-dynamic-metadata-for-blazor-web-assembly/\">Setting dynamic metadata for Blazor Web Assembly</a> - March 23, 2021 - This post shows how HTML header meta data can be dynamically updated or changed for a Blazor Web assembly application routes hosted in ASP.NET Core. This can be usually for changing how URL link previews are displayed when sharing links. <a href=\"https://github.com/damienbod/BlazorMetaData\">Source code</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/damienbod/BlazorMetaData\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":3,\"repo\":\"damienbod/BlazorMetaData\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/stars/damienbod/BlazorMetaData?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=604800\" alt=\"stars\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/last-commit/damienbod/BlazorMetaData?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=86400\" alt=\"last commit\">.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-03-25T08:54:15.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Videos</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8So3TXW2QKU\">Testing Blazor Apps &#x26; Components</a> - March 26, 2021 - Blazor Train, episode 43: Testing Blazor Apps &#x26; Components.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-03-25T08:54:15.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Videos</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wcc14aoylME\">Introduction to Dynamic Components in Blazor</a> - <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Duration:%20-21%20min-%230094FF?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=maxAge&#x26;logo=youtube\" alt=\"duration\"> March 22, 2021 - This video shows how you can use one of the most interesting features in Blazor w/ .NET 6.0 preview which is Dynamic Components. Dynamic Components can help you load content from multiple components dynamically in Blazor without too much hassle. <a href=\"https://github.com/hassanhabib/DynamicComponentBlazorDemo\">Source code</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/hassanhabib/DynamicComponentBlazorDemo\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1,\"repo\":\"hassanhabib/DynamicComponentBlazorDemo\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/stars/hassanhabib/DynamicComponentBlazorDemo?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=604800\" alt=\"stars\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/last-commit/hassanhabib/DynamicComponentBlazorDemo?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=86400\" alt=\"last commit\">.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-03-25T08:54:15.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://codyanhorn.tech/blog/blazor/2021/03/24/Blazor-Excluding-Files-from