 applies to <a href=\"https://zoho.com/bugtracker\">Bugtracker</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/connect\">Connect</a> — Team Collaboration free for 25 users with 3 groups, 3 custom apps, 3 Boards, 3 Manuals, 10 Integrations along with channels,events &#x26; forums.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/meeting\">Meeting</a> — Meetings with upto 3 meeting participants &#x26; 10 Webinar attendees.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/vault\">Vault</a> — Password Management free for Individuals.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/showtime\">Showtime</a> — Yet another Meeting software for training for a remote session upto 5 attendees.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/notebook\">Notebook</a> — A free alternative to Evernote.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/wiki\">Wiki</a> — Free for 3 users with 50 MB storage, unlimited pages, zip backups, RSS &#x26; Atom feed, access controls &#x26; customisable CSS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/subscriptions\">Subscriptions</a> — Recurring Billing management free for 20 customers/subscriptions &#x26; 1 user with all the payment hosting done by Zoho themselves. Last 40 subscription metrics are stored</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/checkout\">Checkout</a> — Product Billing management with 3 pages &#x26; up to 50 payments.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/desk\">Desk</a> — Customer Support management with 3 agents and private knowledge base, email tickets. Integrates with <a href=\"https://zoho.com/assist\">Assist</a> for 1 remote technician &#x26; 5 unattended computers.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/cliq\">Cliq</a> — Team chat software with 100 GB storage, unlimited users, 100 users per channel &#x26; SSO.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/campaigns\">Campaigns</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/forms\">Forms</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https:/zoho.com/sign\">Sign</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/surveys\">Surveys</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/bookings\">Bookings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zoho.com/analytics\">Analytics</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2021-03-25T06:09:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"agarrharr/awesome-cli-apps","categoryHTML":"<h2>Development</h2><h3>Docker</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ivanilves/lstags\">lstags</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ivanilves/lstags\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">281</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":281,\"repo\":\"ivanilves/lstags\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Synchronize images across registries.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-03-25T02:36:19.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"agarrharr/awesome-cli-apps","categoryHTML":"<h2>Development</h2><h3>Docker</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/lirantal/dockly\">dockly</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/lirantal/dockly\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2.8k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":2825,\"repo\":\"lirantal/dockly\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Interactively manage 